window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They walk among us. They look just like us. They plot our doom.</p> <p>Some call them the scummers. Hybrids. Humans with alien DNA.</p> <p>Years ago, they hatched in alien labs. They came to Earth as sleeper agents. Since then, theyâ€™ve been mingling with our society. They teach our children. They cook our food. They tend to our elders. All the while waiting. Biding their time. Hiding in plain sight.</p> <p>And now they strike. With devastating force. With terrifying cruelty. They bring Earth to its knees.</p> <p>But we will rise again. We are humans, brave and proud. And we will fight back!</p>"; 
